The police may have a serial killer on their hands when they locate a second body in a site where the first victim was found several months before.
The body was trussed up in the same way and had an identical burn mark on his back. 
There is no apparent link between the first victim, student Michael Haughty, and the second Jason Villers, a probationer at the police college. 
While the police find evidence that may solve the Haughty case, they have nothing on the Villers murder.
